Can you add a unit test, please? It should be pretty easy to do. Just add smth like
```javascript
   "macros": {
    "a": {
        "type": "macroDef",
        "params": [ { "name": "a", "optional": false, "default": 5 } ],
        "result": "%a%"
      }
    },
    "ret": "@a"
```
in `config_preprocessor_test_errors.json`. Thanks :)
